snippet.title: Special Agent CyberDuck Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.funbit.cyberduck
Apple App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/special-agent-cyberduck/id1556373885

Special Agent CyberDuck, a fun, addictive and action-packed pixelart platform game is available on Android and iOS. 

Designed and develped by @lukasinspace, creator of Cluckles' Adventure.

Stuck on a level, or just want to chat about the game? Check out the official Reddit community:
https://www.reddit.com/r/cyberduckgame/

Twitter: @lukasinspace
Fandom Wiki: https://cyberduck.fandom.com/
Support email: littlegames.funbit(at)gmail.com
Support webpage: https://sites.google.com/view/funbitgames/home

Music by: Nuclear Mushroom Boom
Twitter: @rubel_nmb
Email: rubel.nmboom(at)gmail.com
